      "text": "# ⚔️ The Wide-Net Heavy Blade"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "1f7589a9454a7632",
      "text": "**The Understanding Blade** · `SPELL-LKTFGW-16`"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "8a2943cf111a1ed7",
      "text": "> The weaver who casts a net across seventeen stars does not seek to catch the light, but to define the space where the light is free to dance."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "d76a2cd49c7b442e",
      "text": "Tier **heavy** · Stratum 4/6 · Hex `undefined` · 17 nodes · undefined laps · undefined spells cast · charge **undefined**"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "aaf4554e1f5ebde2",
      "text": "Constellation `undefined` · forged 2026-03-30 · category *understanding*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ac0cc6ec92dbfa7c",
      "text": "**Significance.** Trades speed for structural complexity. 714 transitions create a perimeter so complex no extraction engine can map its centre. The Hole the Wind Cannot Find."
    },
